      "sector": "finance",
      "title": "Payments with EUDI Wallets using SCA",
      "summary": "Purchase ferry tickets from Cyclades Fast Ferries using your EUDI Wallet in a merchant-led payment flow. Powered by iGrant.io, this is the first live EUDI Wallet payment in production, combining Strong Customer Authentication (SCA) with verifiable credentials via 3D Secure and OpenID4VC, using the Visa/Worldline network with Banca Transilvania.",
